%% Approval Amount Thresholds Summary
%% < $500: Auto-approval if within budget
%% $500 - $4,999: Operations Manager approval required
%% $5,000 - $24,999: Division Leader + Operations Manager approval
%% >= $25,000: Executive team approval required
%% Emergency: Special expedited process with post-approval documentation

%% Timeout Rules
%% Operations Manager: 48 hours before escalation
%% Division Leader: 72 hours before executive escalation
%% Executive: 72 hours before CEO escalation
%% CEO: Final authority, no further escalation

%% Integration Points
%% QuickBooks: Automatic sync after approval
%% Email: Notifications at each state change
%% Dashboard: Real-time status updates
%% Audit Trail: Complete approval history logged